    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This plugin is used to display thumbnail images (pdf supported) in a widget.<br />\nThe main difference from other media widgets, is the use of taxonomy shipped with the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/enhanced-media-library\" rel=\"ugc\">Enhanced Media Library</a> plugin</p>\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>filter by categories (using Enhanced Media Lib)</li>\n<li>limit the output of thumbnails</li>\n<li>&#8220;show more&#8221; link to load additional thumbnails</li>\n<li>open in new tab</li>\n<li>hide / show media title</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "installation": "<p>Add it through wordpress or unpack the downloaded zip file into your wp-content/plugins directory</p>\n",
        "changelog": "<p>Release notes are provided by the <a href=\"https://github.com/ole1986/wp-show-media-widget/releases\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Github project page</a></p>\n"
    },
